{"tid":2103473,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPad Pro 上運行 macOS Big Sur 神人實機示範順暢效果","createTime":"2020-07-11T08:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T15:30:08.000Z","uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e32e2f54b33f3315925b1af9c2f859699b6d43c3","tid":2103473,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"最近，外國有網民嘗試在 iPad Pro 上使用 macOS Big Sur 系統，發現使用時能夠和原來的 iPadOS 系統一樣順暢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jsngr/status/1278501414906605576?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjsngr%2Fstatus%2F1278501414906605576%3Fs%3D21&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyIbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=7caa3526\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjsngr%2Fstatus%2F1278501414906605576%3Fs%3D21&h=25bef737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jsngr/status/1278501414906605576?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nApple 早前在 WWDC 2020 上宣布推出 macOS Big Sur，但至今還沒有正式在 iPad 上運行 macOS 系統。網民 Jordan Singer 透過 Twitter 上載測試影片，並稱自己是利用自行編譯的 SwiftUI 模擬在 iPad Pro 內運行 macOS Big Sur。<br />\n<br />\nJordan Singer 雖然沒有為 iPad、iPhone 製作一個真正的 macOS Big Sur 模擬器，但有針對系統進行最佳化，將 UI 介面改成適合觸控螢幕等操作。<br />\n<br />\n隨著 iPadOS 與 macOS 之間的差異已經越來越小，相信 macOS Big Sur 終有機會正式應用於 iPad Pro 上。<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：Twitter"},{"pid":"8888d5e6b60f6cddbebb527c86dad2d7772162d1","tid":2103473,"uid":86378,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"蘋果垃圾，又抄<br />\n得iDog打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31e341950fda3c8c3d7a50d3eb3d7239fe7e0ea","tid":2103473,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T08:40:39.000Z","msg":"Apple Arm成功嘅話，將會帶領消費級電子產品大一統<br />\narm + metal api變成未來趨勢"},{"pid":"56eef60d1ded1173e6e793370d6ae4e95136738d","tid":2103473,"uid":187548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"姐係點 can run mac apps?"}]}